<P>IN the fir&s;t editions of the Gieru&s;alemme liberata, Ta&s;&s;o places the i&s;land of Armida in the pacific ocean; and the de&s;cription of the above con&s;tellation is to be found in the voyage of Ubald and Guelpho round Cape Horn in que&s;t of Rinaldo,</P>
